data.description: Craftsman 4 bedroom 2 bath home built in 2017 by Gene Lantrip! Open floor plan, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, freshly painted, easy-care stained concrete floors throughout! Split bedroom plan, x-large master bdrm, garden tub, sep. shower & has a huge walk-in closet. Backyard is completely fenced with steel posts & cedar wood. You'll love the above-ground gardens--herbs, peppers, green beans, tomatoes, squash, melon, etc! Front yard has a peach tree right before the front door along with other fruit & vegetable plans! Sprinkler system front & back, large storage shed. 2-10 Structure warranty is still in place for another 7 years! 1735 sqft per appraiser--don't delay on this extra special home.
